29
00:03:44,957 --> 00:03:48,423
Only with it we can find the way to our goal, nibbana.

30
00:03:49,104 --> 00:03:53,408
And negligence is the way to repeated cycle of birth and death.

31
00:03:56,073 --> 00:04:02,882
Conscientious people are able to achieve or reach nibbana, thus escaping the rebirths.

32
00:04:04,145 --> 00:04:08,931
